{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"weak"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNOfflineStorageDelegate","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNOfflineStorageDelegate>"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"delegate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An offline storage object sends messages to its delegate to allow it to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"transform URLs before they are requested from the internet. This can be used"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"add or remove custom parameters, or reroute certain requests to other servers"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or endpoints."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/delegate","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/delegate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"delegate","symbolKind":"property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflineStorage(py)delegate","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"delegate","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","fragments":[{"text":"delegate","kind":"identifier"}]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The receiver’s delegate."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"]]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/document